snippet.title: Game Of Throne Airplane Chairs: The Johnny Depp/Amber Heard Saga - Part Two
snippet.description:
Rachael and Kev break down the allegations made toward Johnny Depp by Amber Heard in her recent Motion to Dismiss.

This motion is in response to the defamation lawsuit brought against her by Johnny Depp.

If you like what you see, please like, subscribe and share!
